animeTitle: Eizouken ni wa Te wo Dasu na!
otherNames: Hands off the Motion Pictures Club!, 映像研には手を出すな! ; Keep Your Hands Off Eizouken!
synopsis: Asakusa Midori wants to create an anime, but she's too disheartened to make that first step by herself. By pure chance, she meets Mizusaki Tsubame, an up-and-coming socialite secretly dreaming of becoming an animator. Together with Midori's money-loving best friend Kanamori Sayaka, the energetic trio slowly work towards making their "ultimate world" a reality!
